    "name": "王牌求生",
    "steam_appid": 3332670,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在病毒爆发以后的很多年，幸存的人类再次面临感染者进化带来的危机，为了重返城市并清理越来越危险的感染者，新政府决定采用生存选拔的方式选出优秀的战士，并以这些战士为中心组建作战部队，任何年满18岁的幸存人类均可以参与选拔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将可以选择操控5个不同的角色，在一座小型城市完成为期30天的生存考研，你身后的基地仅能为你提供有限的支援，你需要通过不断的强化自身，合理的选择战利品，达到完成考验的目的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏里，你将会体验到刺激的砍杀，爽快的开枪扫射，爆头的乐趣，激烈的战场支援，以及有趣的方向键节奏击打健身，让我们一起干它丫的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的特色设计：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆战场支援◆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >呼叫战场支援，在合适的时候触发它们，解决你遇到的难题，让战斗更刺激（会随着游戏更新不断增加）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆快乐健身◆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速的正确按下方向键，并且完美的击打，提升你的各项重要属性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆服装战损◆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内的5名角色均有细致的服装战损细节设计，每个角色的服装拥有多达10个阶段的战损效果展现，为你的挑战之旅带来奇特的情趣体验，请注意，如果你一不小心将注意力专注在破烂的衣服上面，那么可能会带来悲剧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/7c6059cdd4992dfa04e29dc01bece212.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/aab1019bc478fc1259f614d242c2ba8b.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/ec8d273d90d725cabbb39f13eb4a86dc.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/d25030194bb685a66846dee827c6e91b.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/01130bf4b45dc5b762c0b35cd3f80910.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/703af337080e8f6988d5aec131ef8d82.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆狙击赚钱◆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过挑战远距离狙击目标，获取到足够多的积分，让战场变得更丰富更疯狂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆配件搭配◆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过合理的搭配配件，让你能够更好的应对当天遇到的敌人和特殊情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/e94b535772d59a22625acee03ab9704d.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是我自己一个人开发的游戏，我无法做到和很多大型游戏媲美，只希望大家能够从我的游戏中感受到新奇的创意和欢乐，我非常乐意接收玩家们的建议，让游戏变得越来越好玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
